TopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jha1665702714162.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jha1665702714162.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jha1665702714162.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jha1665702714162\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Signature Parameter\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Signature Parameter is a Development Object that describes an argument that can be passed in or out of an operation.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jha1665702714162__section_iqv_ng1_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623312e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">opr</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dlk1665702714091.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlk1665702714091.html\" title=\"A Signature Operation is a Development Object that describes the public method of a signature.\">Signature Operation</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jha1665702714162__table_d10790e1_d10791e1_d10792e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">sig:<var class=\"keyword varname\">SignatureName</var>:opr:<var class=\"keyword varname\">OperationName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jha1665702714162__section_lnz_sg1_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623312e238\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jha1665702714162__p_d96773e1_d96774e1_d96775e1\">Signature Parameter specializes Development Object in the\n        following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jha1665702714162__ul_wx4_tg1_nwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jha1665702714162__li_d39365e1_d39366e1_d39367e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jha1665702714162__p_d96776e1_d96777e1_d96778e1\">It has a Signature Operation as parent object.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jha1665702714162__li_d39368e1_d39369e1_d39370e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jha1665702714162__p_d96779e1_d96780e1_d96781e1\">It has no child development objects and no code\n            containers.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613902\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613902\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Signature Parameter Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Signature Parameter A Signature Parameter is a Development Object that describes an argument that can be passed in or out of an operation. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: opr Main Development Object? No Part of: Signature Operation Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: sig: SignatureName :opr: OperationName Specialization Signature Parameter specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a Signature Operation as parent object. It has no child development objects and no code containers. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}